docs {
  # WebSocket Message Format
  
  **PREREQUISITE**: You must run the `Auth/Login` request first to generate a valid `accessToken`.
  
  Send a JSON message to chat:
  ```json
  {
    "type": "MESSAGE",
    "payload": {
      "roomId": "<ROOM_ID>",
      "content": "Hello World",
      "msgType": "TEXT"
    }
  }
  ```
}
